---
/** MockupYaveh — yaInbox conversation with AI handoff + Mentor panel (replicates real product UI) */
---
<div class="yav-frame">
  <!-- Top bar: yaInbox -->
  <div class="yav-topbar">
    <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; flex: 1; min-width: 0;">
      <div style="width: 20px; height: 20px; border-radius: 50%; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #20B2AA, #10B981); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex-shrink: 0;">
        <svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="white"><path d="M21 15a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"/></svg>
      </div>
      <span style="font-size: 9px; font-weight: 700; color: #1F2937; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;">yaInbox</span>
      <span style="font-size: 8px; color: #9CA3AF;">Central de Conversas</span>
    </div>
    <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; flex-shrink: 0;">
      <span style="font-size: 7px; color: #6B7280;">0 Atendimentos ativos</span>
      <span style="font-size: 7px; color: #6B7280;">TMA: 04:32</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Contact header -->
  <div class="yav-contact-bar">
    <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; flex: 1; min-width: 0;">
      <div style="width: 28px; height: 28px; border-radius: 50%; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3B82F6, #1D4ED8); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex-shrink: 0; font-size: 9px; font-weight: 700; color: white;">AB</div>
      <div>
        <div style="font-size: 10px; font-weight: 600; color: #1F2937;">ASF Business Finance</div>
        <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 3px;">
          <svg width="8" height="8" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="#25D366"><path d="M17.472 14.382c-.297-.149-1.758-.867-2.03-.967-.273-.099-.471-.148-.67.15-.197.297-.767.966-.94 1.164-.173.199-.347.223-.644.075-.297-.15-1.255-.463-2.39-1.475-.883-.788-1.48-1.761-1.653-2.059-.173-.297-.018-.458.13-.606.134-.133.298-.347.446-.52.149-.174.198-.298.298-.497.099-.198.05-.371-.025-.52-.075-.149-.669-1.612-.916-2.207-.242-.579-.487-.5-.669-.51a5.8 5.8 0 0 0-.57-.01c-.198 0-.52.074-.792.372s-1.04 1.016-1.04 2.479 1.065 2.875 1.213 3.074c.149.198 2.096 3.2 5.077 4.487.709.306 1.262.489 1.694.625.712.227 1.36.195 1.871.118.571-.085 1.758-.719 2.006-1.413.248-.694.248-1.289.173-1.413-.074-.124-.272-.198-.57-.347z"/></svg>
          <span style="font-size: 7px; color: #22C55E;">WhatsApp Comercial - Waent</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 4px; flex-shrink: 0;">
      <div class="yav-badge-mql">MQL</div>
      <div class="yav-pipeline-dots">
        <span class="yav-pipe">LEAD</span>
        <span class="yav-pipe yav-pipe-active">MQL</span>
        <span class="yav-pipe">SAL</span>
        <span class="yav-pipe">SQL</span>
      </div>
      <div class="yav-badge-mentor">Mentor</div>
      <div class="yav-badge-resolved">Resolvida</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Body: chat + mentor panel -->
  <div class="yav-body">
    <!-- Chat area -->
    <div class="yav-chat">
      <!-- Date separator -->
      <div class="yav-date">2 de fevereiro</div>

      <!-- Client message -->
      <div class="yav-msg-left">
        <div class="yav-bubble-white">
          <div>Confirmar</div>
          <span class="yav-time">10:51</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- AI message -->
      <div class="yav-msg-right">
        <div class="yav-ai-label">
          <svg width="8" height="8" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="#20B2AA"><rect x="3" y="3" width="7" height="7"/><rect x="14" y="3" width="7" height="7"/><rect x="3" y="14" width="7" height="7"/><rect x="14" y="14" width="7" height="7"/></svg>
          <span>IA</span>
        </div>
        <div class="yav-bubble-green">
          <div>Ola! Que otimo que voce demonstrou interesse. Para eu entender melhor como podemos ajudar a ASF Business Finance, poderia me dizer qual o principal desafio que sua equipe enfrenta hoje?</div>
          <span class="yav-time">10:51 <span style="opacity: 0.6;">✓✓</span></span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Client reply -->
      <div class="yav-msg-left">
        <div class="yav-bubble-white">
          <div>Nossa maior dificuldade hoje e em aumentar a quantidade de contato com leads no processo de prospeccao</div>
          <span class="yav-time">10:52</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- AI HANDOFF MESSAGE — HIGHLIGHTED -->
      <div class="yav-msg-right">
        <div class="yav-ai-label">
          <svg width="8" height="8" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="#20B2AA"><rect x="3" y="3" width="7" height="7"/><rect x="14" y="3" width="7" height="7"/><rect x="3" y="14" width="7" height="7"/><rect x="14" y="14" width="7" height="7"/></svg>
          <span>IA</span>
        </div>
        <div class="yav-bubble-handoff">
          <div>Perfeito, o melhor caminho daqui pra frente e voce falar com um de nossos especialistas, entao eu vou te transferir agora para alguem do time e logo eles retornam por aqui ok? Foi um prazer falar com voce! 🚀</div>
          <span class="yav-time-light">10:53 <span style="opacity: 0.6;">✓✓</span></span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Human agent takes over -->
      <div class="yav-msg-right">
        <div class="yav-bubble-green-light">
          <div>Bom dia, tudo bem por ai?</div>
          <div style="margin-top: 3px;">Com que eu falo?</div>
          <span class="yav-time">10:55 <span style="opacity: 0.6;">✓✓</span></span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Client -->
      <div class="yav-msg-left">
        <div class="yav-bubble-white">
          <div>Bom dia Netto</div>
          <span class="yav-time">10:59</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="yav-msg-left">
        <div class="yav-bubble-white">
          <div>Aqui e o Felipe</div>
          <span class="yav-time">11:00</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Human agent continues -->
      <div class="yav-msg-right">
        <div class="yav-bubble-green-light">
          <div>Oi Felipe, bom dia! Tudo bem? 😊</div>
          <div style="margin-top: 3px;">Obrigada por explicar o cenario. Entao hoje o maior desafio e conseguir falar com mais leads no processo de</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Footer -->
      <div class="yav-chat-footer">
        <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 4px;">
          <div style="width: 5px; height: 5px; border-radius: 50%; background: #F59E0B;"></div>
          <span style="font-size: 7px; color: #F59E0B; font-weight: 500;">Janela de 24h fechada</span>
          <span style="font-size: 7px; color: #9CA3AF;">&middot; Envie um template para reabrir</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Sidebar icons -->
    <div class="yav-sidebar-icons">
      <div class="yav-side-icon yav-side-active">
        <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="white"><path d="M12 3L1 9l4 2.18v6L12 21l7-3.82v-6l2-1.09V17h2V9L12 3z"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div class="yav-side-icon"><svg width="11" height="11" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#9CA3AF" stroke-width="1.8"><polygon points="13 2 3 14 12 14 11 22 21 10 12 10"/></svg></div>
      <div class="yav-side-icon"><svg width="11" height="11" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#9CA3AF" stroke-width="1.8"><circle cx="12" cy="8" r="4"/><path d="M6 21v-2a4 4 0 0 1 4-4h4a4 4 0 0 1 4 4v2"/></svg></div>
      <div class="yav-side-icon"><svg width="11" height="11" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#9CA3AF" stroke-width="1.8"><path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z"/></svg></div>
      <div class="yav-side-icon"><svg width="11" height="11" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#9CA3AF" stroke-width="1.8"><path d="M12 20h9"/><path d="M16.5 3.5a2.12 2.12 0 0 1 3 3L7 19l-4 1 1-4L16.5 3.5z"/></svg></div>
      <div class="yav-side-icon"><svg width="11" height="11" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#9CA3AF" stroke-width="1.8"><polyline points="22 12 18 12 15 21 9 3 6 12 2 12"/></svg></div>
    </div>

    <!-- Mentor panel -->
    <div class="yav-mentor">
      <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #F3F4F6; margin-bottom: 10px;">
        <div style="width: 28px; height: 28px; border-radius: 8px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #20B2AA, #14B8A6); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex-shrink: 0;">
          <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="white"><path d="M12 3L1 9l4 2.18v6L12 21l7-3.82v-6l2-1.09V17h2V9L12 3zm6.82 6L12 12.72 5.18 9 12 5.28 18.82 9zM17 15.99l-5 2.73-5-2.73v-3.72L12 15l5-2.73v3.72z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div style="flex: 1;">
          <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 4px;">
            <span style="font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; color: #1F2937;">Mentor de Vendas</span>
            <span style="font-size: 6px; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; background: rgba(249,115,22,0.1); color: #EA580C; font-weight: 600;">Mentor</span>
          </div>
          <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 3px;">
            <div style="width: 4px; height: 4px; border-radius: 50%; background: #22C55E;"></div>
            <span style="font-size: 7px; color: #9CA3AF;">InsideSales Comercial</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Mentor suggestion content -->
      <div style="font-size: 8px; color: #374151; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 10px;">
        Entendo que aumentar a quantidade de contato com leads na prospeccao e um desafio significativo para a ASF Business Finance.
      </div>
      <div style="font-size: 8px; color: #374151; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 10px;">
        Para te ajudar, a InsideSales oferece solucoes que podem otimizar esse processo. Por exemplo, nosso sistema pode ajudar a automatizar o agendamento de follow-ups e a priorizar leads com base no engajamento.
      </div>
      <div style="font-size: 8px; color: #374151; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 12px;">
        Voce ja utiliza alguma ferramenta de automacao de vendas ou CRM atualmente?
      </div>

      <!-- Action buttons -->
      <div style="display: flex; gap: 6px; margin-bottom: 10px;">
        <div class="yav-mentor-btn-outline">Copiar</div>
        <div class="yav-mentor-btn-fill">Usar resposta</div>
      </div>

      <!-- Feedback -->
      <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px;">
        <span style="font-size: 7px; color: #9CA3AF;">Essa sugestao ajudou?</span>
        <div class="yav-feedback-btn">✓ Fez sentido</div>
        <div class="yav-feedback-btn">✕ Nao ajudou</div>
      </div>

      <!-- Input -->
      <div class="yav-mentor-input">
        <span style="font-size: 8px; color: #9CA3AF; flex: 1;">Pergunte ao Mentor...</span>
        <div style="width: 22px; height: 22px; border-radius: 50%; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #20B2AA, #10B981); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;">
          <svg width="9" height="9" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="white"><path d="M2.01 21L23 12 2.01 3 2 10l15 2-15 2z"/></svg>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .yav-frame {
    width: 100%; max-width: 560px; border-radius: 16px;
    box-shadow: 0 12px 48px rgba(0,0,0,0.10), 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.04);
    background: #ffffff; border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  /* Top bar */
  .yav-topbar {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
    padding: 8px 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid #F3F4F6;
  }

  /* Contact bar */
  .yav-contact-bar {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px;
    padding: 8px 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid #F3F4F6;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .yav-badge-mql {
    font-size: 7px; font-weight: 700; color: #22C55E;
    padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 20px; border: 1px solid rgba(34,197,94,0.3);
  }
  .yav-pipeline-dots {
    display: flex; gap: 2px;
  }
  .yav-pipe {
    font-size: 5px; font-weight: 700; color: #D1D5DB; letter-spacing: 0.03em;
  }
  .yav-pipe-active { color: #1F2937; }
  .yav-badge-mentor {
    font-size: 7px; font-weight: 600; color: white;
    padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 20px; background: #8B5CF6;
  }
  .yav-badge-resolved {
    font-size: 7px; font-weight: 500; color: #6B7280;
    padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 6px; border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;
  }

  /* Body layout */
  .yav-body {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 30px 170px;
    min-height: 280px;
  }

  /* Chat */
  .yav-chat {
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; padding: 8px;
    background: #FAFBFC; overflow: hidden;
  }
  .yav-date {
    font-size: 7px; color: #9CA3AF; text-align: center;
    padding: 3px 10px; margin: 4px auto 8px;
    background: white; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid #F3F4F6;
  }
  .yav-msg-left { align-self: flex-start; max-width: 75%; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .yav-msg-right { align-self: flex-end; max-width: 80%; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .yav-bubble-white {
    background: white; border: 1px solid #E5E7EB; border-radius: 0 10px 10px 10px;
    padding: 6px 8px; font-size: 8px; color: #1F2937; line-height: 1.5;
  }
  .yav-bubble-green {
    background: #D1FAE5; border-radius: 10px 0 10px 10px;
    padding: 6px 8px; font-size: 8px; color: #1F2937; line-height: 1.5;
  }
  .yav-bubble-green-light {
    background: #ECFDF5; border-radius: 10px 0 10px 10px;
    padding: 6px 8px; font-size: 8px; color: #1F2937; line-height: 1.5;
  }

  /* HANDOFF BUBBLE — HIGHLIGHTED */
  .yav-bubble-handoff {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #D1FAE5, #A7F3D0);
    border: 1.5px solid #34D399;
    border-radius: 10px 0 10px 10px;
    padding: 8px 10px; font-size: 8px; color: #065F46; line-height: 1.6;
    font-weight: 500;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(16,185,129,0.15);
    position: relative;
  }
  .yav-bubble-handoff::before {
    content: '🔄 Transferencia para humano';
    display: block; font-size: 6px; font-weight: 700; color: #059669;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em; text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 4px; padding-bottom: 3px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(5,150,105,0.15);
  }

  .yav-ai-label {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 3px; justify-content: flex-end;
    margin-bottom: 2px;
  }
  .yav-ai-label span { font-size: 7px; color: #20B2AA; font-weight: 600; }
  .yav-time { font-size: 6px; color: #9CA3AF; float: right; margin-top: 2px; margin-left: 8px; }
  .yav-time-light { font-size: 6px; color: #059669; float: right; margin-top: 2px; margin-left: 8px; }

  .yav-chat-footer {
    margin-top: auto; padding-top: 6px; border-top: 1px solid #F3F4F6;
  }

  /* Sidebar icons */
  .yav-sidebar-icons {
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 4px;
    padding: 8px 2px; border-left: 1px solid #F3F4F6; border-right: 1px solid #F3F4F6;
  }
  .yav-side-icon {
    width: 22px; height: 22px; border-radius: 6px;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  }
  .yav-side-active { background: #20B2AA; }

  /* Mentor panel */
  .yav-mentor {
    padding: 10px; border-top: 3px solid #10B981;
    display: flex; flex-direction: column;
  }
  .yav-mentor-btn-outline {
    font-size: 7px; font-weight: 500; color: #6B7280;
    padding: 4px 10px; border: 1px solid #E5E7EB; border-radius: 6px;
  }
  .yav-mentor-btn-fill {
    font-size: 7px; font-weight: 600; color: white;
    padding: 4px 10px; border-radius: 6px; background: #10B981;
  }
  .yav-feedback-btn {
    font-size: 6px; color: #6B7280; padding: 2px 6px;
    border: 1px solid #E5E7EB; border-radius: 4px;
  }
  .yav-mentor-input {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px;
    padding: 6px 10px; border: 1px solid #E5E7EB; border-radius: 20px;
    margin-top: auto;
  }

  /* Mobile */
  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .yav-body { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .yav-sidebar-icons, .yav-mentor { display: none; }
    .yav-contact-bar { flex-wrap: nowrap; overflow-x: auto; }
  }
</style>
